                <p class="text-sm base-content">Conference talk | 26th International Conference On Computing In High Energy & Nuclear Physics (CHEP) | May 2023 | Norfolk, VA, USA</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm base-content">
                    <li>Slides: <a href="https://indico.jlab.org/event/459/contributions/11486/" class="link link-info">https://indico.jlab.org/event/459/contributions/11486/</a></li>
