        <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
            <div class="p-4 base-100 rounded shadow">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold base-content">Opportunistic extension of a local compute cluster with NEMO resources for HEP workflows</h3>
                <p class="text-sm base-content">Presentation | 14th Annual meeting of the Helmholtz Alliance "Physics at the terascale" | November 2021 | DESY Hamburg, DE (online)</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm base-content">
