                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
            <div class="p-4 base-100 rounded shadow">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold base-content">Search for Higgs‑Boson Pair‑Production in the bbll+ETMiss final state with the ATLAS detector at &Sqrt;s = 13 TeV</h3>
                <p class="text-sm base-content">PhD thesis | May 2023 | Freiburg, DE</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm base-content">
                    <li>Publication: <a href="https://freidok.uni-freiburg.de/data/238604" class="link link-info">https://freidok.uni-freiburg.de/data/238604</a></li>
                </ul>
